User: $10k, moderate, prefers BTC/ETH/SOL
Market: Bull trending

Design:
- BTC 40% = $4000
- ETH 25% = $2500
- SOL 15% = $1500
- BNB 10% = $1000
- Cash 10% = $1000

Reasoning: Bull market supports alt exposure, BTC/ETH core (65%), measured risk, diversified.

Execute: Call execute_trade for each allocation, save strategy.

